<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>WellTegra – Data Solutions for Well Engineering</title>
<meta content="AI-powered planning, performance, and analysis for well intervention." name="description"/>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="welltegra-header-logo.png" rel="icon" type="image/png">
<link href="welltegra-header-logo.png" rel="apple-touch-icon"/>
<link href="manifest.json" rel="manifest"/>
<meta content="#0f172a" name="theme-color">
</meta></link><script>
function toggleMenu() {
  const nav = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');
  nav.classList.toggle('hidden');
}
</script></head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-white font-sans leading-relaxed">
<!-- Header -->
<header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-950 to-sky-900 text-white shadow-md">
<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">

<button class="md:hidden text-white focus:outline-none" onclick="toggleMenu()">
<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewbox="0 0 24 24">
<path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
</svg>
</button>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<img alt="WellTegra Logo" class="w-16 h-16 rounded" src="welltegra-header-logo.png"/>
<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide">WellTegra</h1>
</div>
<nav class="hidden md:flex gap-6 text-sm font-semibold   h i d d e n   m d : f l e x" id="desktop-menu">
<a class="hover:text-cyan-300" href="#planner">Planner</a>
<a class="hover:text-cyan-300" href="#performer">Performer</a>
<a class="hover:text-cyan-300" href="#analyzer">Analyzer</a>
<a class="hover:text-cyan-300" href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav><nav class="md:hidden hidden flex flex-col gap-2 mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white" id="mobile-menu"><a href="#planner">Planner</a><a href="#performer">Performer</a><a href="#analyzer">Analyzer</a><a href="#contact">Contact</a></nav>
</div>
</header>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="text-center py-16 px-4 bg-slate-800">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-cyan-300 mb-4">AI for Well Delivery</h2>
<p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto text-slate-300">
      WellTegra connects your live operational data from platforms like WellView, Sapphire and OpenWells — giving you insight, efficiency and foresight across planning, performance and analysis.
    </p>
</section>
<!-- Placeholder for Planner / Performer / Analyzer Sections -->
<section class="py-16 px-6 bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-700" id="planner">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
<h3 class="text-3xl text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-4">🧠 Planner Module</h3>
<p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
      Plan well interventions with precision using AI-enhanced case history mapping, digital risk matrices,
      and live integration with platforms like Peloton’s WellView and Halliburton’s OpenWells.
    </p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-400 ml-4">
<li>Pre-filled digital checklists based on historical well configurations</li>
<li>Integration-ready with real-time planning software</li>
<li>AI risk forecasting for common failure scenarios</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-16 px-6 bg-slate-800 border-b border-slate-600" id="performer">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
<h3 class="text-3xl text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-4">⚙️ Performer Module</h3>
<p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
      Monitor and guide operations in real time — whether it's slickline, braided line, wireline, or coiled tubing.
      The Performer module is engineered to reduce NPT and improve crew efficiency.
    </p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-400 ml-4">
<li>Live dashboard for wellsite operations synced to planner</li>
<li>Smart alerts for toolstring configuration errors</li>
<li>On-site decision trees for escalating interventions</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-16 px-6 bg-slate-900" id="analyzer">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
<h3 class="text-3xl text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-4">📊 Analyzer Module</h3>
<p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
      Unlock insights from previous jobs. Compare toolstring performance, track NPT root causes, and visualize
      lessons learned across operations — fueling continuous improvement.
    </p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-400 ml-4">
<li>Generate heatmaps of equipment failures by depth &amp; stage</li>
<li>Auto-tag lessons learned by asset or intervention type</li>
<li>Export summaries for internal audits or client reports</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-400 text-center py-8">
    © 2025 WellTegra Network. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
